Insider Activity


Individual




Ivor J. Evans



Mr. Ike J. Evans is Executive Chairman at Meritor, Inc., Operating Partner at HCI Equity Partners LLC, Operating Partner at Thayer Capital Partners/Blum & Associates and Independent Director at Textron, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at Spirit AeroSystems, Inc., Textron, Inc. and Power & Composite Technologies, Inc. 
Mr. Evans was previously employed as Independent Director by Spirit AeroSystems Holdings, Inc., Chairman by Roadrunner Transportation Services Holdings, Inc., Vice Chairman by Union Pacific Corp., President & Chief Operating Officer by Union Pacific Railroad Co., Senior VP-Industrial Components & Equipment by Emerson Electric Co., President by Blackstone Corp., and a Principal by General Motors Corp. He also served on the board at Roadrunner Transportation Systems, Inc., Cooper Industries Ltd., Boeing Co /Wichita & Tulsa Division/, Roadrunner Dawes, Inc. and Suntron Corp. 
He received his undergraduate degree from Kansas State University. 



